\ Create the code for "next" in the user area
\ compile-in-user-area

here-t
mlabel >next  assembler
userarea-t dp-t !
   ax lods

\+ rel-t  up ax add   0 [ax] bx mov   up bx add   bx jmp
\- rel-t  0 [w] jmp
   nop nop nop nop nop
end-code
dp-t !
